<note n="0325001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0325001">〔即〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0325005" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0325005">陵＝凌【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
